Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you miraculous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, please enjoy a different kind \Nof ending featuring mother and son!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:26.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is Japan's foremost luxury train,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:28.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the Royal Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I quite like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:36.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I wanted to reserve the \Nwhole train for you, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:41.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I wanted to come in \Ncontact with the Japanese people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,if even just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to \Nmeet that famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}What?! You contact Superintendent \NChaki directly yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:54.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Inspector Nakamori, \Nwho is in charge of your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm busy! Get it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Tell Superintendent Chaki that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I mean the visitor I had \Nin my private room earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The bandit known as Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:44.27,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Crystal Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Your Majesty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:52.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He appeared to steal the treasure \Nof the Principality of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:56.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Europe's biggest topaz,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,this Crystal Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:07.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the advance notice sent \Nto the embassy was genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:11.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But why didn't he take off\N with that jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he realized it at the first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That this is only a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A replica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've got the real one\N hidden elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:33.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell you that, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:37.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He could be listening in from \Nsomewhere on this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Kid is on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Check every passenger from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:44.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:53.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I cannot subject everyone else to \Ntrouble for the sake of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a showdown between him and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This train will reach Osaka \Nin two and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:08.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to steal the jewel,\N as stated in his notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or will I be able to protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a duel with the honor \Nof my country on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your necklace is a little strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What a naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I've instructed you countless times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Address me as "Your Majesty" \Nin front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:40.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The son of Queen Selizabeth and King Henry, \Nwho passed away from illness two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He is the next king of the \NPrincipality of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...this replica is different \Nfrom the last time I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a listening device!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:03.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid must have planted it in \NHer Majesty's room when he slipped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:12.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm around, you won't \Nlay a finger on that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:19.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, you certainly have sharp eyes, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You have a weird expression on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That third-rate inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your old man just reamed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wanted to \Nride this train, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked my dad\N to get us tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:47.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. I'm always \Ngrateful to your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! You need an attitude adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And do it before we meet Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, we're on the \Nsame train as a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aren't we lucky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So we'll pay her our respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:05.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce myself as the daughter of \NInspector Nakamori, who always stymies Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:12.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:19.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid has ignored our warning again \Nand is targeting another Big Jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:25.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And thanks to his advance notice, \Nthere are even more security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances, I believe it'll \Nbe tough getting the gem before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In that case, just steal it from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kill him if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But whatever you do, be careful \Nhow you handle that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, it may contain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:50.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...the stone of life, Pandora, \Nwhich can grant immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now will you tell me where \Nyou're keeping the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Without knowing the location, I don't \Nknow where to focus security efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:21.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're that worried about it, \Nthen stay by my side and protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:25.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me pour you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:29.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No thank you, I can't \Ndrink while on duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:35.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh. This is the first time anyone's \Nturned down a drink from me, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Well, in that case, \NI'll indulge in just one drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:08:00.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,European liquor is tops, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's drinking booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:14.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, this is my daughter, \NAoko, and her classmate, Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Charming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's a pleasure to meet you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you two doin' over here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kaito said he really wanted \Nto meet Her Majesty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't innerfere with security \Nby wandering aroun'! {sic}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is he supposed to be protecting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I've managed to infiltrate \NHer Majesty's salon car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so now I can search \Nfor the jewel all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But where the heck could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:59.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was just in Her Majesty's room a little \Nwhile ago, so I doubt she left it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then maybe it's near her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In her bag or under her hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:13.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's in that cat's eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've been gazing at Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! I was looking at the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Her Majesty's cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't he? He'll be two this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:34.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Phillip Maximilian du Ingram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...the prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:52.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, Caesar. \NYou wanted to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Does he hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess that's not really possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a cute teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was a present from my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? One eye is about to fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:34.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't feel like it's in here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Kid the Phantom Thief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't even joke about \Nsomething like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:54.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What, I'm wrong? Too bad, since \NI know where the jewel is hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm not gonna tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Prince Phillip, it's dangerous \Nfor you to be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Return to your room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go on. You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna help Mother \Nprotect the jewel from Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So you're doing it out of \Nlove for your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I hate Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:33.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She changed after Father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She used to be so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:41.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but now, she gets angry and yells\N every time she sees me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She says I never listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know she doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I made Father a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:55.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I promised to protect \Nthe country with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not "Mother"! You call me "Your Majesty"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,- Y-Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd better not see you \Nout of this room again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you have to be so harsh with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's none of your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the only way to \Nget through to that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be arriving in Osaka in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems I've won, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:04.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So where is the jewel hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when we reach Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be surprised, \Nthough, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:20.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where is it? Where the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:25.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! If I don't hurry, \NI'll miss my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, the form changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got it! I know where the jewel is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I need you to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:10.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't be Kid the Phantom Thief\N in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's a blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It must be Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's finally showin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was just tryin' to protect Her Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget that, Inspector. Where's your glass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My glass is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Which one is your glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:14:59.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Start looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:11.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean the jewel was \Nin my glass with the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's some audacity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crystal Mother is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:43.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to see you again, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:48.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're on a train. There's \Nnowhere for you to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, please remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief \Nis an elusive rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And as for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:07.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you're a mother \Nwith a heart before you're a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:07.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come back, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:21.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, get on the phone and have the \Npolice set up a cordon around the whole area!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:29.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you've still got the \Nbooze in your brain, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:32.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,To be fooled by that dummy... \NHow gullible can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's gullible, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The people in my country need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You know, brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:56.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I am impressed you managed \Nto climb up here by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A man helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:04.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said you were sure to be here\N and carried me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look, the nice man standing \Nright behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:19.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't have \Ntime to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Put the jewel down and turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unless you want me to blow \N{\i1}this{\i0} kid's brains out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't the Pandora jewel you \Nand your pals are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I held it up to the moon a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm gonna check it out myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the end of the line for the \Nimmortal Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Negishita Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:43.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Negishita Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:00.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that the attitude you take \Nwith the guy who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Without that jewel, \Nthe people in my country will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:13.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget it! I'm not giving \Nit back to any liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're really doing it for \Nyour mother's sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You wanna return the jewel in \Nthe hope that she'll praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So, am I on the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I've got a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:39.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A way to confirm your mother's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:48.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My country's precious treasure \Nwas stolen because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What will the people say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:02.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I chased Kid the Phantom Thief onto the \Nroof and tried to take back the jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but he got it away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:24.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why won't you ever listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:28.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you always pull \Ndangerous stunts like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:37.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With your father gone, why did I harden my \Nheart and try to give you a strict upbringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:08.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your mom is the genuine Queen of Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, a boy mustn't bawl his eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:17.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And as I keep telling you, \Nrefer to me as "Your Highness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:38.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A magic trick that unlocked \NHer Majesty the Queen's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But tonight, I was \Nno more than the assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The star was a brave little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:48.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:24.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakamori with the Metro Police! \NAnd I'm in charge of this preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:25.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So as for next week's plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:31.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a Detective Delon from Europe goes over \Nmy head and claims he's gonna arrest Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:35.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, this means I've gotta go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:40.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NThe Princess and the Thief's Improv.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:40.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Princess and the Thief's Improv
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:42.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is it? I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, don't miss my exploits!
